          </svg></div></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.detroitnews.com%2fin-depth%2fbusiness%2fautos%2f2019%2f12%2f18%2fgreed-driven-alliance-fca-uaw-leaders-sparks-decade-corruption%2f2634016001%2f" class="facebook pull-quote-share-button" target=_blank rel="noreferrer noopener" title="Share on Facebook" data-analytics-event-on-click=in-depth-pull-quote-facebook-click-2679740001><div class=facebook-button-content><span class=button-text>Share</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 21 20">
